<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Floricultura Natureza Viva | Design Sustentável</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        <nav class="navbar" role="navigation" aria-label="Menu Principal">
            <div class="logo">Natureza<span>Viva</span></div>
            <div class="accessibility-controls">
                <button onclick="changeFontSize(1)" aria-label="Aumentar fonte">A+</button>
                <button onclick="changeFontSize(-1)" aria-label="Diminuir fonte">A-</button>
                <button onclick="toggleContrast()" id="contrast-toggle" aria-label="Alternar Alto Contraste">
                    🌓 Contraste
                </button>
            </div>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <main>
        <section class="hero" aria-labelledby="hero-title">
            <div class="hero-content reveal">
                <h1 id="hero-title">A beleza que brota da terra</h1>
                <p>Descubra espécies raras e dicas de cultivo para transformar seu ambiente.</p>
                <a href="#catalogo" class="btn-primary">Ver Catálogo</a>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="catalogo" class="section-padding" aria-labelledby="cat-title">
            <h2 id="cat-title" class="section-title reveal">Nossas Espécies</h2>
            <div id="flower-grid" class="grid-container reveal">
                </div>
        </section>

        <section class="section-padding bg-soft" aria-labelledby="faq-title">
            <h2 id="faq-title" class="section-title reveal">Cuidados Básicos</h2>
            <div id="faq-container" class="accordion-container reveal">
                </div>
        </section>
    </main>

    <footer class="footer">
        <p>&copy; 2023 Natureza Viva - Design focado em Acessibilidade</p>
    </footer>

    <script src="script.js"></script>
</body>
